How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Amazon Customer
4.0 out of 5 stars Color isn’t quite “Cinnamon”, more like Burgundy and size has changed.
Reviewed in the United States on October 19, 2020
First off, I’m 5’-10” and 140lbs with long arms and I wear the size Medium in this newer version of the Rival hoodie. I used to wear a size large in the old version of this hoodie with the square fabric UA logo that was stitched around the edges (this new one is a rubber/plastic square logo that appears to be ironed on). That being said, the Cinnamon color isn’t even close to the photo...the photo makes it look like a red/brown. The actual hoodie just looks like a plain Jane burgundy to me. I wouldn’t have bought it had I known that. Other than that, it fits good and is warm. I ended up exchanging it for the Mechanic Blue, which is also lighter than the photos unfortunately. Still like the hoodie though, it fits well and is warm. Not super thick, so I usually wear a thermal under it when I will be out in the colder weather.
